overview:
We are one of the best fine pitch gear & cutting tools gear Manufacturer and exporter with helical gears, spur helical gears, industrial helical gears, gear grinding and thread grinding.

Backed by our engineering excellence, we have been able to manufacture and export a vast range of dimensionally accurate machine components such as gears, helical gears, spur helical gears, industrial helical gears, non metallic gear, hob cutters, thread rolling dies, fine pitch ground gears, knurling tools, taps, lead screws, worm and worm wheel, thread milling cutters and rack cutters.
